        "text": "Jeremiah 2:14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), the ‘sons of the handmaids’ (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 23:12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), who rose into more confidential service, the ",
        "children": []
